c: 11
v: 7
t: "Kuma shi ne wanda Ya halicci sammai da ƙasa a cikin kwanaki shida, kuma Al'arshinSa ya kasance akan ruwa, dõmin Ya jarrabã ku, wannan ne daga cikinku mafi kyãwon aiki. Kuma haƙĩƙa idan ka ce: \"Lalle kũ waɗanda ake tãyarwa ne a bãyan mutuwa,\" haƙĩƙa waɗanda suka kãfirta sunã cẽwa: \"Wannan bai zama ba fãce sihiri bayyananne"